      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, really sets the mood. can we get a bit more specific with the details? i want to give the reader a better sense of the people in this area to really lean into that \"social decay\" vibe. like, can you describe some of the characters walking through or hanging out there? maybe describe what they look like, what they're wearing, and the kind of energy they're bringing to the street so i can cast them better.",
